headline: Jabil and AVL Collaborate on Design and Manufacturing Solutions for Automotive and Transportation Customers
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., May 21, 2025--Jabil Inc. (NYSE: JBL), a global manufacturing solutions provider to market-leading automakers, today announced it has signed a memorandum of understanding (MOU) with AVL Software and Functions GmbH, the e-drive and software center of AVL List GmbH.
